WEBVTT

00:11:59.003 --> 00:12:01.619
And this revolution is not just for women.

00:12:01.643 --> 00:12:03.825
Anyone who has been disenfranchised,

00:12:03.849 --> 00:12:06.205
anyone whose story has not been told,

00:12:06.784 --> 00:12:08.064
the same principles apply,

00:12:08.088 --> 00:12:10.694
and I really hope we can do
the revolution together.

00:12:12.392 --> 00:12:13.610
My four-point plan.

00:12:14.371 --> 00:12:16.967
Number one: watch movies.

00:12:16.991 --> 00:12:18.475
Isn't this a good revolution?

00:12:18.499 --> 00:12:19.569
(Laughter)

00:12:19.593 --> 00:12:22.152
OK, first I want to talk to anyone
who watches movies.

00:12:22.176 --> 00:12:23.810
Who watches movies in here?

00:12:23.834 --> 00:12:24.985
Great!

00:12:25.009 --> 00:12:29.014
Will you pledge to watch one film
by a female filmmaker per month?

00:12:29.038 --> 00:12:31.109
That's it, just start there. Great!